snippet.title: 100% Orange Juice - Sweet Creator Character Trailer
snippet.description:
The enigmatic Sweet Creator, leader of Sweet Gods, is here! Turn the battlefield into a field of sweets at the creator's whim, and indulge friends and enemies in countless, irresistible sweets... Sweet Creator is voiced by Ootsubo Yuka!

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2242260/100_Orange_Juice__Sweet_Gods_Pack
